snippet.title: Pluto Lost Its Colors! [Gameplay Trailer 1]
snippet.description:
Introducing the latest platformer video game by NINES™ - Pluto Lost Its Colors! Available now to wishlist on Steam and Epic Games. Pluto's peaceful existence was disturbed when it was attacked by a menacing Black Hole, losing its colors in the ensuing battle. Help Pluto reclaim its color by collecting color shards spread across the galaxy.

https://pluto.ninesconnect.com

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2935260/Pluto_Lost_Its_Colors/
https://store.epicgames.com/p/pluto-lost-its-colors-4fb4c4
